ROADMAP

GOALS
=====
Create tools, scripts to make it easier for other people to use data.
Work toward 10 minute installs and creation of update data (not counting load time).
Want people to be up and running with data in less than one hour. 


GENERAL
=======
1. Build an example import package to MySQL.
2. Build import packages for SQL-Lite, Oracle, Sybase, SQL-Server, Access
3. Automate change control if there is a change in the field structures.
4. Create scripts for autoloading data each night, showing changes in data
5. Create Quickstart de-normalized data products, like ownership on stations
6. Create automated builds of virtual machines with info
7. Create video screencasts of how to get started, video explanations of data tables.


